officialTitle: Modified Luteal Support for Frozen-Thawed Embryo Transfer - A Prospective Study
inclusionCriteria:
* 20-40 years old women
* Spontaneously ovulating women
* Treated in our IVF unit for frozen-thawed embryo transfer
* At least one top quality embryo
* Must be FEMALE
* Must have minimum age of 20 Years
* Must have maximum age of 40 Years
exclusionCriteria:
* PGD patients
* More than 4 previous embryo transfers
